headline: Milliman analysis: Competitive pension risk transfer cost declines to 100.1% during October
summary: SEATTLE, November 18, 2025--Milliman, Inc., a premier global consulting and actuarial firm, today announced the latest results of its Milliman Pension Buyout Index (MPBI). During October, the estimated cost to transfer retiree pension risk to an insurer in a competitive bidding process decreased from 100.5% to 100.1% of a plan’s accounting liabilities (accumulated benefit obligation, or ABO). That means the estimated retiree PRT cost is now 100.1% of a plan’s ABO.

headline: Ethiopian Airlines selects RTX's Collins Aerospace for premium seating solutions across multiple fleets
summary: Collins Aerospace, an RTX (NYSE: RTX) business, signed an agreement with Ethiopian Airlines at the Dubai Air Show to provide premium lie-flat business class seating solutions across Ethiopian's number of fleet of Airbus A350 and Boeing 737 MAX aircraft.
